                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Cache-Control: no-cache&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;Cache-Control: private&lt;/code&gt; clash - you should never get both together: the former tells browsers and proxies not to cache at all, the latter tells proxies not to cache but lets browsers hold their own private copy. I&apos;m not sure which setting the browser will follow, but it&apos;s unlikely to be consistent between browsers and versions.&lt;/span&gt;

