            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@porneL, will you be submitting a competing answer that deals with these myths correctly?&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/8014/oddthinking&quot; title=&quot;23,014 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Oddthinking&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment164443_91512&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2008-11-28 01:56:23Z, License: CC BY-SA 2.5&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Nov 28, 2008 at 1:56&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

