              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/53597/mike-ottum&quot; title=&quot;1,233 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Mike Ottum&lt;/a&gt;
