            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@porneL: No the do not overwrite previously set values as he pass false as a 2nd parameter, telling to not override previous values.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/232831/julien-palard&quot; title=&quot;7,691 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Julien Palard&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment20851565_49557&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2013-02-14 10:52:59Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Feb 14, 2013 at 10:52&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@JulienPalard the answer has been edited after I made my comment. It still doesn&apos;t make much sense.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/27009/kornel&quot; title=&quot;94,731 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Kornel&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment20885253_49557&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2013-02-15 10:31:21Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Feb 15, 2013 at 10:31&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
