            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I don&apos;t know what will be the behavior of the Apache with this config :  - Pragma/Cache-Control has the same role and you give them 2 differents configs. It&apos;s weird. - no-store mean that the ressource should not be cached. So how can it be revalidated ?&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/4616753/camille-gerin-roze&quot; title=&quot;4,121 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;Camille Gerin-Roze&lt;/a&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment113854231_21753925&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2020-10-16 10:05:25Z, License: CC BY-SA 4.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Oct 16, 2020 at 10:05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
